lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我追問佢朋友 <br />\n原來佢喺唔夠兩星期內同左2個人ons 1個人hook up準備踏入新既關係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而我掂下佢搏頭都覺得被侵犯</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/corrupttheyouth.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/21389201_10156488261964045_244990892_o.jpg?resize=640%2C934\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fcorrupttheyouth.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F21389201_10156488261964045_244990892_o.jpg%3Fresize%3D640%252C934&h=d59dc3bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ed1859c577c5c7791ce1eeb16e92669cb3e2c9","tid":1155231,"uid":115655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"自己揀嘅邊怪得人<br />\n抵死啦唔揀毒西"},{"pid":"a730e4130329e589fefb85c8f67849973155abe9","tid":1155231,"uid":195333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6858geu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6858geu.jpg&h=848c2ac3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10365124835cd4b7aded453a62761e6d205ff6ae","tid":1155231,"uid":145226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39da29532fbd3bc93e4c1816189bcfa5a1241437","tid":1155231,"uid":139251,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T23:45:28.000Z","msg":"喺呢一切發生之前 佢係一個正常女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕對相信佢冇偷食過<br />\n不過條友顛撚到 食毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我以前同佢講隊草都屌9佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"我想問你同佢係邊個國家一齊住？<br />\n隊草